properties.Name: ChannelAggregateProductBookings
properties.Description:
The total Product bookings expressed in terms of unit quantity and booked valuation for the associated timestamp.

Bookings are field sales reports of anticipated sales that must be planned for in terms of inventory and also provide management with anticipated sales revenues.    In this case bookings are summarized for a product across all customers.

Columns.Name: ChannelId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Channel.

Columns.Name: ProductId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Product.

Columns.Name: Timestamp
Columns.Description: The timestamp that the associated information is reported, recorded or effective as-of.

Columns.Name: TotalBookedProductUnitsQuantity
Columns.Description: The total quantity of Product booked for the associated date.

Columns.Name: TotalBookedProductUnitsInvoicedAmount
Columns.Description: The total valuation of Product booked during the associated period and valued at actual invoiced values as of the associated date.

Columns.Name: IsoCurrencyCode
Columns.Description:
The ISO 4217 currency code.

Ex:
Currency Code = AED
Currency Name = Dirham
Country Name = United Arab Emirates
